Thwack (https://jontopielski.itch.io/thwack)
===========

Original version by:  
https://github.com/jontopielski/thwack-jam  
https://jontopielski.itch.io/thwack (ThwackLinux.zip, Apr 28 2023 release)

Description 
===========

Funky-legged tennis game. Thwack demo/jam files are already included and ready to go. The full game is available for purchase at https://jontopielski.itch.io/thwack. To run the full game, down ThwackLinux.zip, extract it, and copy the Thwack.pck file into the gamedata directory. The full version includes 8 enemies to face, each with unique court challenges, 3 difficulty modes, local multiplayer, and cool hats.

To compile:
===========

wget https://downloads.tuxfamily.org/godotengine/3.5.0/godot-3.5.0-stable.tar.xz  
tar xf godot-3.5.0-stable.tar.xz  
cd godot-3.5.0-stable/platform  
git clone https://github.com/Cebion/frt.git  
cd ../  
scons platform=frt tools=no target=release use_llvm=yes module_webm_enabled=no -j12  
strip bin/godot.frt.opt.llvm

Controls:
===========

DPAD/ANALOG = Movement  
A/B         = Thwack it

